column5: hit the west pier about 12am fished till 4am had a few bumps, a couple guys on the east pier hooked a couple and landed a few, oh well thats pier fishin, i'll be back down there fri night again to give it another go. cheers
i walked down at bronte yesturday with my son and the guys i talked to were not catching anythng.  seems its still to early.  cheers!
